section: 5. Working Metrics (last run snapshot)

text: Carried forward run-to-run so the agent can detect drift. Updated by amendment after each run; not authoritative against the ledger.

metric: Unreconciled rate | value: 0.31 | unit: percent | target: 0.5 | trend: down | period: 2026-06
metric: Drafts awaiting human gate | value: 7 | trend: flat | period: 2026-06-24
metric: Largest pending draft | value: 184500 | unit: QAR | period: 2026-06-24
